reviewText: I am quite happy with this DVD. It lives up to its promise of giving an overview. I have the Balciki tapes which show a lot of technique and this dvd helped me understand that one even better. It could have been longer but I think it is a fair amount of the material for the price. The qaulity of the packaging and the menus are also quite good.
This allowed me an overview of this particular art and training. Glad I bought these. Haven't seen all related programs.
